---
source: cli/tests/help.rs
expression: "help(&[\"subvolume\", \"find-new\"])"
---
List the recently modified files in a subvolume

Prints all files that have been modified since the given generation number. The generation can be
found with `btrfs subvolume show`.

Usage: find-new <PATH> <LAST_GEN>

Arguments:
  <PATH>
          Path to the subvolume to search

  <LAST_GEN>
          Only show files modified at or after this generation number

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
